Brooklyn College Labor Education Center; and the Hope Shapiro Bread and Roses Award from New Jersey Peace Action, in honor of her commitment to peace and social justice and her tireless work to protect and expand voter rights.  In 2014, she received the prestigious Puffin Prize for Creative Citizenship from the Puffin and Nation Institutes.	2016-08-25 17:40:19.354196	\N	f	f	1	http://www.gc.cuny.edu/Page-Elements/Academics-Research-Centers-Initiatives/Doctoral-Programs/Political-Science/Faculty-Bios/Frances-Fox-Piven	
