ny Magazine's 100 most influential black Americans from 1980 to 1984. In 1987, the Coalition of Black Trade Unionists established the Addie L. Wyatt Award.\n\n	2016-08-25 17:40:23.22572	\N	f	f	1	http://cluw.org/My%20Pics/In%20Memoriam/Wyatt.jpg	https://www.youtube.com/embed/8oEDABGqxRw
